1. Use following command to build vdht image, which vdht source code can make compilation:

     sudo docker build -t mytest1 .
 
   If vdht image want to be remake without involving cache, the command can changed to be:
     sudo docker build --no-cache -t mytest1 . 

2. Use following command to start run vdhtd container
   
     sudo docker run -d mytest1 /run.sh

